      { speaker: 'Doctor', en: 'I see. Do you have any other symptoms, like fever or pain in your body?', zh: '我明白了。你还有其他症状吗，比如发烧或者身体疼痛？' },
      { speaker: 'You', en: 'No fever, but my neck and shoulders feel a little sore.', zh: '没有发烧，但我的脖子和肩膀有点酸痛。' },
      { speaker: 'Doctor', en: 'That might be from stress or sitting too long. Do you sleep well at night?', zh: '那可能是压力或者坐太久引起的。你晚上睡得好吗？' },
      { speaker: 'You', en: 'Not really. I can\'t fall asleep easily, and I wake up many times.', zh: '不太好。我很难入睡，而且会醒很多次。' },
      { speaker: 'Doctor', en: 'I understand. Have you tried anything to help you relax, like warm tea or deep breathing?', zh: '我理解。你有没有试过什么方法来放松，比如喝热茶或者深呼吸？' },
      { speaker: 'You', en: 'I drink coffee sometimes, but maybe that\'s not good, right?', zh: '我有时候喝咖啡，但可能不太好，对吧？' },
      { speaker: 'Doctor', en: 'Coffee can keep you awake, so it\'s better to avoid it in the evening. Water or herbal tea is nicer.', zh: '咖啡会让人保持清醒，所以晚上最好避免喝。水或者花草茶更好。' },
      { speaker: 'You', en: 'Okay, I will try that. But I also feel dizzy when I stand up fast.', zh: '好的，我会试试。但我快速站起来的时候还会头晕。' },
      { speaker: 'Doctor', en: 'Dizziness could mean low blood pressure or not eating enough. Do you eat regular meals?', zh: '头晕可能意味着低血压或者没吃够东西。你按时吃饭吗？' },
      { speaker: 'You', en: 'I skip breakfast a lot because I\'m in a hurry.', zh: '我经常因为赶时间而不吃早餐。' },
      { speaker: 'Doctor', en: 'That can make you tired and dizzy. Try to have a small breakfast, like fruit or yogurt.', zh: '那会让你感到疲劳和头晕。试着吃一点早餐，比如水果或者酸奶。' },
      { speaker: 'You', en: 'I will try that. Should I come to see a doctor for a check-up?', zh: '我会试试的。我需要来看医生做个检查吗？' },
      { speaker: 'Doctor', en: 'Yes, if your symptoms don\'t get better in a few days, it\'s a good idea to visit a clinic.', zh: '是的，如果几天后你的症状没有好转，去诊所看看是个好主意。' },
      { speaker: 'You', en: 'Thank you. You helped me understand what to do.', zh: '谢谢你。你帮我明白了该怎么做。' },
      { speaker: 'Doctor', en: 'You\'re welcome! Take care of yourself, and I hope you feel better soon.', zh: '不客气！照顾好自己，希望你早日好转。' },
      { speaker: 'You', en: 'Thanks doctor! I\'ll follow your advice and come back if it doesn\'t get better. Have a nice day!', zh: '谢谢医生！我会听从你的建议，如果没好转再回来。祝你今天愉快！' }
