      { speaker: 'Staff', en: 'Exactly! You can say: \'Are there monthly fees or service charges?\' That shows you\'re smart about money.', zh: '没错！你可以说：“有月费或服务费吗？”这显示你对钱很精明。' },
      { speaker: 'You', en: 'Thanks! I\'ll remember. And after I open the account, can I get a debit card right away?', zh: '谢谢！我会记住的。开户后，我能马上拿到借记卡吗？' },
      { speaker: 'Staff', en: 'Usually yes! They\'ll say: \'Your card will arrive in 5-7 business days.\' Or sometimes they give it on the spot.', zh: '通常可以！他们会说：“你的卡会在5到7个工作日内寄到。”或者有时当场给你。' },
      { speaker: 'You', en: 'Oh, I hope I get it fast. What if I lose it? Can I report it at the bank?', zh: '哦，我希望快点拿到。如果我丢了怎么办？可以在银行挂失吗？' },
      { speaker: 'Staff', en: 'Definitely! You can call or go to the branch. Just say: \'I lost my debit card. Can you block it?\'', zh: '当然可以！你可以打电话或去分行。就说：“我丢了借记卡。你能冻结它吗？”' },
      { speaker: 'You', en: 'Perfect. I think I can do it now. Let me try a full practice from start?', zh: '完美。我想我现在可以了。让我从头完整练习一遍？' }
